      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h1 id=&#34;github-pages-documentation-website-plan&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        GitHub Pages Documentation Website Plan&#xA;    &lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#github-pages-documentation-website-plan&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: GitHub Pages Documentation Website Plan&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: GitHub Pages Documentation Website Plan&#34; href=&#34;#github-pages-documentation-website-plan&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;overview&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Overview&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#overview&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Overview&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Overview&#34; href=&#34;#overview&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Create a small documentation website hosted on GitHub Pages to present all the backlog project documentation in an organized, searchable format.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;website-structure--navigation&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Website Structure &amp;amp; Navigation&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#website-structure--navigation&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Website Structure &amp;amp; Navigation&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Website Structure &amp;amp; Navigation&#34; href=&#34;#website-structure--navigation&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;main-navigation&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Main Navigation&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#main-navigation&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Main Navigation&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Main Navigation&#34; href=&#34;#main-navigation&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Home&lt;/strong&gt; - Project overview and quick start&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Getting Started&lt;/strong&gt; - Installation and basic usage&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CLI Reference&lt;/strong&gt; - Auto-generated command documentation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AI Integration&lt;/strong&gt; - MCP server setup and usage&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Development&lt;/strong&gt; - Architecture, analysis, and contribution guide&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About&lt;/strong&gt; - Project inspiration and credits&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;content-organization&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Content Organization&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#content-organization&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Content Organization&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Content Organization&#34; href=&#34;#content-organization&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;code&gt;content/&#xA;├── _index.md          # Home page (from README.md)&#xA;├── getting-started.md # Quick start guide&#xA;├── cli/               # CLI reference (existing)&#xA;│   ├── _index.md&#xA;│   ├── backlog.md&#xA;│   ├── backlog_create.md&#xA;│   └── ... (other CLI docs)&#xA;├── ai-integration.md  # MCP integration guide&#xA;├── development/       # Development docs&#xA;│   ├── _index.md&#xA;│   ├── architecture.md&#xA;│   ├── analysis.md    # Existing technical analysis&#xA;│   └── plan.md        # Existing project plan&#xA;└── about.md           # Project background&#xA;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;technical-approach&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Technical Approach&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#technical-approach&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Technical Approach&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Technical Approach&#34; href=&#34;#technical-approach&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;static-site-generator-hugo&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Static Site Generator: Hugo&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#static-site-generator-hugo&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Static Site Generator: Hugo&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Static Site Generator: Hugo&#34; href=&#34;#static-site-generator-hugo&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Hugo&lt;/strong&gt;: Fast builds, excellent GitHub Pages support, powerful theming&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Theme&lt;/strong&gt;: Use a clean, documentation-focused theme (Docsy, Book, or Geekdoc)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Features&lt;/strong&gt;: Built-in search, syntax highlighting, mobile-responsive, taxonomies&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;implementation-steps&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Implementation Steps&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#implementation-steps&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Implementation Steps&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Implementation Steps&#34; href=&#34;#implementation-steps&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Initialize Hugo site with &lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt; configuration&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Select and configure a documentation theme&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Create content structure and organize existing documentation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Set up GitHub Actions for automated deployment&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Configure custom domain and search functionality&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;key-features&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Key Features&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#key-features&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Key Features&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Key Features&#34; href=&#34;#key-features&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Automatic CLI docs&lt;/strong&gt;: Integrate existing CLI documentation&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Built-in search&lt;/strong&gt;: Hugo&amp;rsquo;s native search functionality&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mobile responsive&lt;/strong&gt;: Modern, accessible design&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lightning fast&lt;/strong&gt;: Sub-second build times&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Easy maintenance&lt;/strong&gt;: Markdown-based content with front matter&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;task-breakdown&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        Task Breakdown&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#task-breakdown&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: Task Breakdown&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: Task Breakdown&#34; href=&#34;#task-breakdown&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;flex align-center gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;t15---github-pages-documentation-website&#34;&#xA;    &gt;&#xA;        T15 - GitHub Pages Documentation Website&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;    &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;http://localhost:1313/backlog/development/plan/#t15---github-pages-documentation-website&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center&#34; title=&#34;Anchor to: T15 - GitHub Pages Documentation Website&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor to: T15 - GitHub Pages Documentation Website&#34; href=&#34;#t15---github-pages-documentation-website&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;svg class=&#34;gdoc-icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Priority&lt;/strong&gt;: High&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Labels&lt;/strong&gt;: documentation, website, github-pages, hugo&#xA;&lt;strong&gt;Description&lt;/strong&gt;: Create a small documentation website hosted on GitHub Pages to present all the backlog project documentation in an organized, searchable format for both human users and AI agents.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
